properties.headline: Lakeshore Flood Advisory issued February 3 at 3:31AM CST until February 4 at 6:00PM CST by NWS Chicago IL
properties.description:
The National Weather Service in Chicago has issued a Lakeshore
Flood Advisory...which is in effect from midnight tonight to 6 PM
CST Tuesday.

* WINDS AND WAVES...North northeast winds to 30 mph are expected
to build waves of 8 to 11 ft.

* TIMING...Tonight and Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Flooding and beach erosion area possible in flood
prone and low lying areas along the Lake Michigan shoreline of
Lake County Illinois.
properties.instruction:
A Lakeshore Flood Advisory indicates that onshore winds will
generate flooding of low areas along the lakeshore.

NWSheadline: LAKESHORE FLOOD ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM MIDNIGHT TONIGHT TO 6 PM CST TUESDAY
